title: BRIEF-Starboard Files Definitive Proxy Materials To Elect Four Highly Qualified Director Nominees To The Newell Board Of Directors
text:
Market News April 11, 2018 / 1:27 PM / in 9 minutes BRIEF-Starboard Files Definitive Proxy Materials To Elect Four Highly Qualified Director Nominees To The Newell Board Of Directors Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 11 (Reuters) - Newell Brands Inc: 
* FILES DEFINITIVE PROXY MATERIALS TO ELECT FOUR HIGHLY QUALIFIED DIRECTOR NOMINEES TO THE NEWELL BOARD OF DIRECTORS AT THE UPCOMING 2018 ANNUAL MEETING 
* “URGES” NEWELL SHAREHOLDERS TO VOTE BLUE PROXY CARD TO ELECT ALL FOUR OF ITS NOMINEES Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
